            <title>[SPR-2440] Pleaes adjust JIRA settings to obscure/hide my email address.</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-2440</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to the JIRA website, the way to obfuscate email addresses is in global JIRA configuration settings. Please do this. Thank you.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
